    <div class="shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
}
```

## Z Index Scale

### Canonical Z Layers
```css
:root {
  --z-base: 0;
  --z-dropdown: 1000;
  --z-sticky: 1100;
  --z-fixed: 1200;
  --z-modal-backdrop: 1300;
  --z-modal: 1400;
  --z-popover: 1500;
  --z-tooltip: 1600;
  --z-toast: 1700;
}
```

