"z-[var(--z-toast)]"
```

## Prohibited Patterns

### Theme Specific Shadows
```css
/* FORBIDDEN: Themes cannot override shadows */
[data-theme="my-theme"] {
  --shadow-sm: 0px 10px 20px ...;  /* System constant */
}
```

### Hardcoded Shadow Values
```rust
