### Violation 3: Domain Deciding Business Rules
```rust
// ❌ WRONG
#[component]
pub fn WorkflowView() -> impl IntoView {
    view! {
        {if status == "Active" {  // ❌ UI deciding rules
            view! { <button>"Complete"</button> }
        } else {
            view! { <span>"Not available"</span> }
        }}
    }
}
