## Summary

**Golden Rule:** Orchestrators coordinate, never implement.

**Pattern:**
```
Domain (READ) ← Orchestrator → Commands (WRITE)
```

**Orchestrator responsibilities:**
- ✅ Refresh triggers
- ✅ Callbacks
- ✅ Layout
- ✅ Optimistic updates

**Never:**
- ❌ Business logic
- ❌ Complex rendering
- ❌ Database access
- ❌ Heavy computation

**Keep orchestrators:**
- Small (< 100 lines)
- Simple (coordination only)
- Testable (mock both sides)

