## Summary

**Golden Rule:** Context Provider eliminates prop drilling for global state.

**Pattern:**
```
Provider (top) → provide_context()
    ↓
Consumer (any depth) → use_context()
```

**When to Use:**
- ✅ Multiple consumers
- ✅ Deep nesting
- ✅ Global state (selection, theme, user)

**Benefits:**
- ✅ Zero prop drilling
