## Migration Guide

### Before (Forbidden)
```rust
view! {
    {is_visible.then(|| view! {
        <div>"Content"</div>
    })}
}
```

### After (Canonical)
```rust
view! {
    <Show when=move || is_visible>
        <div>"Content"</div>
    </Show>
}
```

### Before (Nested)
```rust
view! {
    {user.is_some().then(|| view! {
        {user.unwrap().is_admin.then(|| view! {
            <AdminPanel />
        })}
    })}
}
```

### After (Canonical)
```rust
view! {
    <Show when=move || user.is_some()>
        <Show when=move || user.unwrap().is_admin>
            <AdminPanel />
        </Show>
    </Show>
}
```

